title: I AM ATHLETE: Antoine Walker & Wale Ogunleye on How To Make 100 Million
description:
I AM ATHLETE | Season 3: Episode 21

Brandon Marshall and D.J. Williams welcome former NBA superstar Antoine Walker and UBS Global Wealth Management's Adewale "Wale" Ogunleye in episode 21 of I Am Athlete. Watch as Antoine and Wale discuss their personal journeys with finance and the disparity in black financial literacy.
